txt.en: Consume Consumables: Orange Wyandotte Carrying Chicken

Orange Wyandotte Carrying Chickens can be bartered for Hobnanigans Tokens or Buried Treasure Tokens during either event.\n\nYou should use an Orange Wyandotte Carrying Chicken many times to accomplish this deed.
